    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p><p>Get all your ingredients and equipment ready</p><p>Skim through these steps, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Note: Equipment and pan sizes vary. Make sure you cook food thoroughly (even if it takes you a little longer than 10 min)</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-sardinian-style-lamb-and-chilli-spaghetti/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>lamb mince</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 4 min or until beginning to brown, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-sardinian-style-lamb-and-chilli-spaghetti/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and slice your<strong> shallot[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>tomato paste</strong>,<strong> red wine paste </strong>and<strong> beef stock mix</strong> in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>dried oregano </strong>and most of your <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) \u2013 this is your<strong> spicy stock</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-sardinian-style-lamb-and-chilli-spaghetti/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the lamb has begun to brown, add the <strong>sliced shallot</strong> to the pan and cook for 1-2 min or until starting to soften</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-sardinian-style-lamb-and-chilli-spaghetti/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> quick cook spaghetti </strong>to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong>, then bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>spaghetti</strong> for 2-3 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>spaghetti</strong>, reserving a cup of the<strong> starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-sardinian-style-lamb-and-chilli-spaghetti/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the shallot has softened, add your<strong> roasted garlic paste</strong> to the pan<strong> </strong>and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>spicy stock</strong> to the pan, reduce the heat to medium and cook for a final 3 min or until thickened and the lamb is cooked through (no pink meat!) \u2013 this is your <strong>spicy</strong> <strong>lamb & chilli sauce</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-sardinian-style-lamb-and-chilli-spaghetti/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> cooked spaghetti</strong> to the <strong>spicy</strong> <strong>lamb & chilli sauce </strong>with a splash of<strong> starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Mix it all together and cook for a final 1 min or until the sauce is coating the spaghetti \u2013 this is your <strong>spicy Sardinian-style lamb & chilli spaghetti</strong></p><p>Tip: Add another splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry!</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/spicy-sardinian-style-lamb-and-chilli-spaghetti/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> spicy Sardinian-style lamb & chilli spaghetti</strong> topped with your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Sprinkle the <strong>remaining chilli flakes</strong> over the spaghetti (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and season with a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
